<Verbatim PAsource="" >"handicap system </Verbatim>
<Rewrite PAsource="" >for bets" - he was only bluffing.</Rewrite>


<Verbatim PAsource="" >The Sun's QC George Carman said: 'You are a goalkeeper who keeps moving the goalposts. </Verbatim>
